Zero Trust security in microservices requires multiple layers:

28
00:01:41,995 --> 00:01:46,406
mTLS for service-to-service encryption and authentication.

29
00:01:46,406 --> 00:01:50,637
JWT with short-lived tokens for user authentication.

30
00:01:50,637 --> 00:01:55,552
Service mesh (Istio) for network policies and authorization.

31
00:01:55,552 --> 00:01:58,822
Vault for secrets management with dynamic credentials.

32
